text: Repeated customer, have been coming here since last year, with sister and friends. Amazing massage and amazing people even though its like under block and not the high class end massage looking parlour. Favourite masseuse would be Lela, Baby and Julia, they listen to every concern you have in order to relieve pain and help body aches. Truly recommended. Did massage, foot reflexology and even cupping. Very affordable.

The staff are friendly and their massage skills are good. In particular one by the name of Aily. She had helped me to improve on my frozen shoulder from unable to move my left arm to restore back to normal. I will recommend anyone who had this issue to her.
Good 25min shoulder massage! I had slight tension in my shoulder and much better after massage üëçüèª

I got myself a full body massage here. Highly recommend BB here for a great Massage.  She gave me  good advice on my pulled nerve recovery and showed attentive care to ensure my comfort during the massage.

I requested for someone who knows how to do a proper shoulder massage for me but ended up receiving one of the worst massages I had in my life. Had a very poor masseuse who knows nothing about removing knots from shoulders and did a sloppy job. Told the masseuse which part of my body needed more massage but she kept on pressing other areas.
